1
00:00:17,472 --> 00:00:20,149
Why did you have to join
the Black Blood Gang?

2
00:00:21,275 --> 00:00:22,526
I joined the gang

3
00:00:23,653 --> 00:00:25,738
not to save myself.

4
00:00:27,823 --> 00:00:29,116
I joined them

5
00:00:29,533 --> 00:00:31,202
to protect our friends...

6
00:00:33,037 --> 00:00:34,455
Matt is one lucky guy

7
00:00:34,872 --> 00:00:36,666
to have a friend like you.

8
00:00:37,667 --> 00:00:39,627
I want to be as lucky as him one day.

9
00:00:41,879 --> 00:00:43,296
Aren't you curious

10
00:00:43,297 --> 00:00:44,757
why Raze has been quiet lately?

11
00:00:49,053 --> 00:00:50,930
Why don't you ask him yourself?

12
00:00:51,681 --> 00:00:53,599
Stay away from Supremo

13
00:00:54,141 --> 00:00:55,267
or you die.

14
00:00:56,060 --> 00:01:00,898
I'm not going to let you or
Supremo's stupidity ruin everything!

15
00:01:02,191 --> 00:01:04,485
The night you and your friend got poisoned.

16
00:01:06,028 --> 00:01:07,530
I kept something from you.

17
00:01:08,155 --> 00:01:09,865
A student requested it from me.

18
00:01:15,454 --> 00:01:18,207
A student you know well.

19
00:01:21,085 --> 00:01:22,085
Jerome

20
00:01:25,172 --> 00:01:26,424
where were you that time?

21
00:01:32,179 --> 00:01:32,680
Zein!

22
00:01:32,681 --> 00:01:34,180
You’re too much!

23
00:01:34,181 --> 00:01:36,892
Isn't it the perfect timing?

24
00:01:38,102 --> 00:01:41,105
You took the liquor and the ice

25
00:01:41,814 --> 00:01:42,982
and came back

26
00:01:43,065 --> 00:01:44,545
and all of the sudden we're poisoned?

27
00:01:45,568 --> 00:01:46,568
Am I right?

28
00:01:47,653 --> 00:01:48,863
But wait

29
00:01:49,905 --> 00:01:51,615
you weren't alone, were you?

30
00:01:52,575 --> 00:01:54,034
Someone was with you.

31
00:01:54,368 --> 00:01:55,411
Do you remember?

32
00:01:57,872 --> 00:01:59,498
Do any of you remember?

33
00:02:00,082 --> 00:02:01,709
What are you saying?

34
00:02:03,961 --> 00:02:05,004
Jerome

35
00:02:07,173 --> 00:02:08,758
where were you that night?

36
00:02:09,425 --> 00:02:10,426
What did you do?

37
00:02:10,551 --> 00:02:11,677
What are you saying, Zein?

38
00:02:11,844 --> 00:02:12,844
Do you remember?

39
00:02:14,513 --> 00:02:15,890
Where were you that night?

40
00:02:17,808 --> 00:02:18,976
What did you do?

41
00:02:30,237 --> 00:02:31,781
You don't want to talk?

42
00:02:35,910 --> 00:02:37,369
You requested it, didn't you?

43
00:02:38,370 --> 00:02:40,164
Can you remember now?

44
00:02:40,706 --> 00:02:44,043
You requested the poison we ingested.

45
00:02:46,605 --> 00:02:47,564
Admit it!

46
00:02:47,589 --> 00:02:49,423
- You poisoned us!
- You're right!

47
00:02:50,471 --> 00:02:52,256
I placed the ice!

48
00:02:54,694 --> 00:02:56,569
I did that because she warned me

49
00:02:56,594 --> 00:02:58,513
that Madam Violet will harm you!

50
00:03:00,142 --> 00:03:01,142
Who's she?

51
00:03:02,186 --> 00:03:03,186
Huh?

52
00:03:03,437 --> 00:03:04,437
Who is it?

53
00:03:04,939 --> 00:03:06,857
Who told you, Jerome?

54
00:03:08,192 --> 00:03:09,192
The student

55
00:03:10,984 --> 00:03:12,235
with the red hood.

56
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,466
The one who helped us in the clinic.

57
00:03:19,322 --> 00:03:21,157
To help Zein and Dave.

58
00:03:30,047 --> 00:03:32,382
She told me that Francisco
and Madam Violet

59
00:03:32,383 --> 00:03:34,881
were planning to poison Zein.

60
00:03:39,306 --> 00:03:41,517
We weren't sure how or when

61
00:03:42,017 --> 00:03:44,697
but we had a hunch that they'll
do it during the acquaintane party.

62
00:03:45,563 --> 00:03:47,439
We needed to act fast.

63
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:51,193
I know it sounds crazy.

64
00:03:52,528 --> 00:03:54,738
But we needed to poison
Zein with a less fatal dose.

65
00:04:02,621 --> 00:04:04,874
That was the only way to save her

66
00:04:05,249 --> 00:04:07,459
without drawing suspicion
from Madam Violet.

67
00:04:24,226 --> 00:04:27,358
The only way to protect
her was to strike first.

68
00:04:30,274 --> 00:04:31,483
Where's the antidote?

69
00:04:33,986 --> 00:04:35,738
Please take care of her.

70
00:04:49,710 --> 00:04:54,214
I placed the poison inside the
ice to lessen the potency.

71
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:57,468
But I didn't expect that she
would drink so much that night.

72
00:04:59,303 --> 00:05:00,554
Zein.

73
00:05:18,948 --> 00:05:21,742
Now, let her drink the antidote.

74
00:05:26,747 --> 00:05:29,816
I promise I didn't know
it would turn out that bad.

75
00:05:30,918 --> 00:05:32,336
Even Dave got poisoned.

76
00:05:33,462 --> 00:05:34,463
I'm sorry.

77
00:05:35,089 --> 00:05:36,089
Sorry, okay?

78
00:05:36,382 --> 00:05:37,382
Sorry.

79
00:05:38,954 --> 00:05:40,235
I screwed up, okay!

80
00:05:40,260 --> 00:05:41,136
You're an asshole!

81
00:05:41,137 --> 00:05:42,220
Aren't we your friends?

82
00:05:42,221 --> 00:05:43,471
- Why didn't you tell us?
- Matt, enough!

83
00:05:43,472 --> 00:05:44,807
- Matt!
- Stop it!

84
00:05:44,808 --> 00:05:46,141
Matt, stop!

85
00:05:46,892 --> 00:05:47,892
Stop it, bro.

86
00:05:48,143 --> 00:05:48,994
Matt!

87
00:05:49,019 --> 00:05:50,019
Asshole.

88
00:05:51,563 --> 00:05:53,189
You should be the
one to understand

89
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:56,068
if Jerome had a secret
he was protecting.

90
00:05:57,042 --> 00:05:58,042
So...

91
00:05:58,788 --> 00:05:59,998
I wasn't the target.

92
00:06:14,128 --> 00:06:15,128
The bottle

93
00:06:16,422 --> 00:06:17,662
someone tossed it to us, right?

94
00:06:20,509 --> 00:06:21,509
The girl.

95
00:06:25,723 --> 00:06:26,723
Is that so...

96
00:06:28,434 --> 00:06:29,434
we have someone on our side

97
00:06:29,435 --> 00:06:30,978
we know nothing about.

98
00:07:00,382 --> 00:07:02,760
Incineration protocol.

99
00:09:56,517 --> 00:09:57,601
Can I sit here?

100
00:10:01,104 --> 00:10:02,981
So much for asking.

101
00:10:05,025 --> 00:10:07,110
You really don't know
how to be afraid, do you?

102
00:10:08,487 --> 00:10:10,405
Why should I be afraid of you, Frtizy?

103
00:10:11,406 --> 00:10:12,741
As expected

104
00:10:13,158 --> 00:10:15,869
from a secretary spoiled by Supremo.

105
00:10:17,537 --> 00:10:19,748
What the hell do you want, Fritzy?

106
00:10:20,975 --> 00:10:23,310
There a few things I want to clarify.

107
00:10:23,335 --> 00:10:24,335
Please.

108
00:10:24,753 --> 00:10:26,880
I don't have time for your nonsense.

109
00:10:29,132 --> 00:10:30,801
Even if it's for Supremo's sake?

110
00:10:35,764 --> 00:10:37,891
What do you really want to say, Frtizy?

111
00:10:38,433 --> 00:10:39,433
Look...

112
00:10:40,310 --> 00:10:42,980
I was a bitch to you before
because I was testing you.

113
00:10:43,897 --> 00:10:45,816
But believe it or not

114
00:10:46,358 --> 00:10:48,527
we want the same thing.

115
00:10:49,444 --> 00:10:51,655
And that's protecting Supremo.

116
00:10:54,116 --> 00:10:56,118
How do I know if I could trust you?

117
00:10:56,827 --> 00:10:58,869
I believe that he's the only hope

118
00:10:58,870 --> 00:11:00,789
for all of us to escape this place.

119
00:11:02,499 --> 00:11:03,499
Yes.

120
00:11:04,543 --> 00:11:06,253
I know I was a bitch to you sometimes.

121
00:11:06,628 --> 00:11:07,628
Sometimes?

122
00:11:08,588 --> 00:11:11,133
But I also want to get
out of this hellhole.

123
00:11:12,384 --> 00:11:13,384
So...

124
00:11:15,012 --> 00:11:16,430
let's work together.

125
00:11:23,895 --> 00:11:24,895
Fine.

126
00:11:26,064 --> 00:11:30,694
But you need to respect
my position as SSG Secretary.

127
00:11:31,945 --> 00:11:33,488
Enough with you bullshit.

128
00:11:36,616 --> 00:11:37,616
Fine.

129
00:11:37,743 --> 00:11:41,330
Just make sure that you'll use
your position to your advantage.

130
00:11:42,122 --> 00:11:43,122
Of course.

131
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:45,125
But just so you know

132
00:11:45,792 --> 00:11:47,502
this doesn't mean that we're friends.

133
00:11:50,380 --> 00:11:51,465
We just have a deal.

134
00:11:52,341 --> 00:11:53,341
Deal!

135
00:11:55,469 --> 00:11:56,469
Lunch?

136
00:12:12,986 --> 00:12:14,237
There's a policy here

137
00:12:15,238 --> 00:12:17,032
gorgeous first.

138
00:12:17,366 --> 00:12:18,366
So...

139
00:12:18,992 --> 00:12:20,410
wait behind me.

140
00:12:26,458 --> 00:12:27,709
Remember

141
00:12:28,126 --> 00:12:31,046
we're not supposed to
be seen as friends.

142
00:12:31,421 --> 00:12:32,631
Chill.

143
00:12:32,881 --> 00:12:34,674
I'm just getting a drink.

144
00:12:35,509 --> 00:12:36,843
I'm not planning to stay.

145
00:12:37,511 --> 00:12:38,511
Duh!

146
00:12:53,235 --> 00:12:54,235
A queen?

147
00:12:55,862 --> 00:12:58,280
I have a feeling that my bag will fall

148
00:12:58,281 --> 00:13:00,283
and will leave a mess on the floor.

149
00:13:08,458 --> 00:13:09,918
I knew it!

150
00:13:10,419 --> 00:13:12,796
My intuition is so strong, isn't it?

151
00:13:13,463 --> 00:13:14,798
Pick it up for me.

152
00:13:19,511 --> 00:13:20,511
Zein.

153
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:25,016
This makes me so happy.

154
00:13:25,308 --> 00:13:27,644
My slaves instantly multiplied!

155
00:13:28,562 --> 00:13:30,021
As they should

156
00:13:30,397 --> 00:13:32,649
I'm the queen of this school anyway.

157
00:13:40,365 --> 00:13:43,368
I'm feeling something else coming.

158
00:13:43,910 --> 00:13:44,536
Wow.

159
00:13:44,661 --> 00:13:45,787
Don't you feel

160
00:13:46,371 --> 00:13:47,913
that a hand is going to smack

161
00:13:47,914 --> 00:13:51,543
that foundation filled face of yours?

162
00:13:52,919 --> 00:13:56,298
I see where Zein gets her audacity from.

163
00:13:57,090 --> 00:13:58,758
And you are?

164
00:13:59,217 --> 00:13:59,634
Oh

165
00:14:00,093 --> 00:14:01,678
You don’t have to know me.

166
00:14:02,345 --> 00:14:04,848
And I don’t care about you anyway.

167
00:14:05,098 --> 00:14:06,414
How dare you...

168
00:14:08,143 --> 00:14:08,994
Oops.

169
00:14:09,019 --> 00:14:10,019
Sorry.

170
00:14:10,228 --> 00:14:11,313
I couldn't help it.

171
00:14:13,064 --> 00:14:14,107
Let's go, Zein.

172
00:14:18,069 --> 00:14:19,154
Get out of the way!

173
00:14:19,821 --> 00:14:20,989
Move!

174
00:14:23,533 --> 00:14:24,533
Deserve.

175
00:14:24,785 --> 00:14:26,281
Nice one, Mia.

176
00:14:26,762 --> 00:14:30,432
We should've slapped
her on each cheek.

177
00:14:30,558 --> 00:14:31,951
You take the left and

178
00:14:31,976 --> 00:14:33,227
I'll take the right.

179
00:14:33,376 --> 00:14:34,961
At least you landed one on her.

180
00:14:35,045 --> 00:14:37,047
Way to show her you
can't be bossed around.

181
00:14:37,172 --> 00:14:38,881
But I think I slapped her too hard.

182
00:14:38,882 --> 00:14:40,050
She deserved it!

183
00:14:40,675 --> 00:14:42,469
What if she takes revenge
on you, Mia?

184
00:14:43,720 --> 00:14:46,931
And does more something worse?

185
00:14:46,932 --> 00:14:48,475
Then I'll slap her again.

186
00:14:49,184 --> 00:14:50,519
On the other side of her cheek.

187
00:14:50,602 --> 00:14:51,453
To even it out.

188
00:14:51,478 --> 00:14:52,020
Mia.

189
00:14:52,021 --> 00:14:53,355
Mia's gotten a lot braver.

190
00:14:54,356 --> 00:14:55,982
Don't worry about me, Zein.

191
00:14:56,691 --> 00:14:58,151
I can handle myself.

192
00:14:58,922 --> 00:15:00,841
Mia has grown so much.

193
00:15:01,154 --> 00:15:03,990
Version 2.0!

194
00:15:04,157 --> 00:15:05,408
- Yeah!
- Stop it.

195
00:15:05,492 --> 00:15:06,492
Nice one, Mia.

196
00:15:09,329 --> 00:15:10,329
May I sit?

197
00:15:10,664 --> 00:15:11,664
Let's go, guys.

198
00:15:11,789 --> 00:15:12,582
Let's go?

199
00:15:12,582 --> 00:15:13,565
We still have class.

200
00:15:13,590 --> 00:15:14,870
- Right? Class?
- Yeah, let's go.

201
00:15:15,054 --> 00:15:16,453
- Oh right class.
- Class.

202
00:15:16,920 --> 00:15:18,713
We don't want to be late so.

203
00:15:18,755 --> 00:15:20,130
We’ll go now, Zein. Bye bye.

204
00:15:20,131 --> 00:15:21,007
Bye, Zein!

205
00:15:21,008 --> 00:15:22,092
How about you, Angelica?

206
00:15:22,175 --> 00:15:24,052
Do you want to walk with us?

207
00:15:26,179 --> 00:15:27,680
Come on! Give me your bag.

208
00:15:27,681 --> 00:15:28,682
Let's go.

209
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:50,161
You're still not eating enough?

210
00:15:53,081 --> 00:15:54,457
What do you call this?

211
00:15:56,835 --> 00:15:57,836
It's food, isn't it?

212
00:15:59,129 --> 00:16:00,130
That's food?

213
00:16:00,797 --> 00:16:01,797
Obviously.

214
00:16:02,048 --> 00:16:03,048
You should try it.

215
00:16:04,259 --> 00:16:05,635
Am I an animal?

216
00:16:06,595 --> 00:16:08,430
You don't eat vegetables?

217
00:16:13,059 --> 00:16:14,394
You're going to make me eat

218
00:16:14,769 --> 00:16:16,062
bermuda grass?

219
00:16:16,688 --> 00:16:17,688
And

220
00:16:18,815 --> 00:16:19,815
what is this?

221
00:16:19,983 --> 00:16:21,109
Bitter melon.

222
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,403
That sounds bad.

223
00:16:24,321 --> 00:16:26,406
Stop acting like a spoiled kid.

224
00:16:26,615 --> 00:16:27,591
What?

225
00:16:27,616 --> 00:16:28,635
No, I'm not.

226
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:31,162
Grown men eat vegetables.

227
00:16:32,675 --> 00:16:35,219
And what is your scientific
explanation for that?

228
00:16:36,541 --> 00:16:38,293
Scientific explanation, really?

229
00:16:38,568 --> 00:16:39,694
Just try it!

230
00:16:42,236 --> 00:16:45,156
You're not going to get
full if you just stare at me

231
00:16:45,553 --> 00:16:46,721
or my food.

232
00:16:49,679 --> 00:16:50,679
But I feel like

233
00:16:51,431 --> 00:16:52,599
your gaze is enough

234
00:16:53,224 --> 00:16:54,517
to keep me full.

235
00:16:59,898 --> 00:17:01,024
Are you going to eat

236
00:17:01,358 --> 00:17:02,567
or should I feed you?

237
00:17:05,362 --> 00:17:06,362
Why not?

238
00:17:07,155 --> 00:17:08,782
I'm a spoiled kid after all.

239
00:17:10,408 --> 00:17:11,409
You wish.

240
00:17:12,327 --> 00:17:13,662
Just try it.

241
00:17:14,579 --> 00:17:15,579
Come on.

242
00:17:17,916 --> 00:17:19,417
I got my hope's up in you feeding me.

243
00:17:21,378 --> 00:17:22,879
Are you going to eat

244
00:17:23,838 --> 00:17:25,215
or else...

245
00:17:25,507 --> 00:17:26,507
Or else what?

246
00:17:59,708 --> 00:18:00,708
Zein.

247
00:18:02,585 --> 00:18:03,585
Zein?

248
00:18:06,589 --> 00:18:08,425
It's so good.

249
00:18:09,718 --> 00:18:10,719
You should try it.

250
00:18:14,723 --> 00:18:15,723
Come on.

251
00:18:17,225 --> 00:18:18,476
Bitter melon.

252
00:18:19,894 --> 00:18:20,895
It's yummy!

253
00:18:34,826 --> 00:18:35,826
This tastes horrible.

254
00:18:35,827 --> 00:18:36,953
Don't spit it out!

255
00:18:39,748 --> 00:18:40,748
Very good.

256
00:18:41,916 --> 00:18:42,916
Try this one.

257
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:46,212
You already know what this is called.

258
00:18:47,839 --> 00:18:48,839
- What is it?
- Spinach.

259
00:18:50,133 --> 00:18:51,133
Correct.

260
00:18:51,468 --> 00:18:52,468
Try it.

261
00:18:53,178 --> 00:18:54,512
I don't eat spinach.

262
00:18:55,722 --> 00:18:56,805
Just try it.

263
00:18:56,806 --> 00:18:57,807
One bite.

264
00:18:58,391 --> 00:18:59,391
Promise

265
00:18:59,434 --> 00:19:00,434
it's not bitter.

266
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:03,020
Try it.

267
00:19:24,417 --> 00:19:25,417
Oh?

268
00:19:28,379 --> 00:19:29,379
Ace...

269
00:19:29,422 --> 00:19:30,422
Huh?

270
00:19:30,965 --> 00:19:31,965
Are you okay?

271
00:19:34,761 --> 00:19:35,761
Supremo

272
00:19:37,347 --> 00:19:38,389
are you okay?

273
00:19:40,892 --> 00:19:41,976
Thank you for the lunch.

274
00:19:42,727 --> 00:19:43,727
Zein.

275
00:19:43,853 --> 00:19:44,896
Are you...

276
00:19:45,355 --> 00:19:46,856
allergic to spinach?

277
00:19:47,232 --> 00:19:48,775
Why didn't you tell me!

278
00:19:49,317 --> 00:19:50,276
Supremo.

279
00:19:50,276 --> 00:19:51,276
It's okay.

280
00:19:52,153 --> 00:19:53,153
Zein

281
00:19:54,489 --> 00:19:55,532
it tastes good.

282
00:19:57,283 --> 00:19:58,284
Just like what you said.

283
00:20:02,622 --> 00:20:03,665
Supremo...

284
00:20:03,998 --> 00:20:04,998
I could never

285
00:20:06,501 --> 00:20:07,794
waste your efforts.

286
00:20:11,673 --> 00:20:14,717
Even if my body refuses.

287
00:20:17,262 --> 00:20:18,262
Please...

288
00:20:18,388 --> 00:20:19,388
please!

289
00:20:19,597 --> 00:20:20,598
Please drink!

290
00:20:21,099 --> 00:20:22,099
Help!

291
00:20:23,101 --> 00:20:24,101
Help us!

292
00:20:24,602 --> 00:20:25,770
Please!

293
00:20:27,021 --> 00:20:28,105
Please!

294
00:20:28,106 --> 00:20:28,606
- Help us!
- What happened?

295
00:20:28,606 --> 00:20:29,274
Supremo...

296
00:20:29,524 --> 00:20:30,524
Help!

297
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:34,090
Let's take him to the clinic, please!

298
00:20:35,530 --> 00:20:36,573
Supremo, please!

299
00:20:36,865 --> 00:20:38,241
Please, help us!

300
00:20:42,829 --> 00:20:44,122
Please help us!

301
00:20:44,289 --> 00:20:45,123
Nurse Cha, please!

302
00:20:45,123 --> 00:20:46,363
- What happened?
- It's Supremo.

303
00:20:46,541 --> 00:20:47,709
He...

304
00:20:48,626 --> 00:20:51,421
He ate spinach and had
a sudden allergic reaction.

305
00:20:52,714 --> 00:20:53,714
Let him lie down.

306
00:20:54,674 --> 00:20:55,674
Now!

307
00:20:59,178 --> 00:21:00,178
Is he...

308
00:21:00,221 --> 00:21:01,221
Is he.

309
00:21:01,306 --> 00:21:02,306
Is he going to.

310
00:21:02,765 --> 00:21:03,765
To live?

311
00:21:04,017 --> 00:21:05,101
Of course he is!

312
00:21:06,477 --> 00:21:07,729
You're going to be okay.

313
00:21:27,332 --> 00:21:28,332
He's stable now.

314
00:21:28,583 --> 00:21:30,460
He needs further observation.

315
00:21:33,213 --> 00:21:34,213
Stupid!

316
00:21:34,505 --> 00:21:36,215
You put Supremo in danger!

317
00:21:36,341 --> 00:21:36,841
I didn't mean to.

318
00:21:36,841 --> 00:21:37,775
You're such an idiot!

319
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:38,568
Stupid!

320
00:21:38,593 --> 00:21:39,569
Can't you do anything right?

321
00:21:39,594 --> 00:21:40,361
Idiot!

322
00:21:40,386 --> 00:21:41,279
Stop it!

323
00:21:41,304 --> 00:21:42,304
Angel!

324
00:21:43,014 --> 00:21:46,851
You wouldn’t like it if Supremo
knew you slapped his secretary!

325
00:21:48,478 --> 00:21:51,105
I'm sure Supremo will punish
her personally when he wakes up.

326
00:21:52,607 --> 00:21:54,067
She's lucky if he doesn't kill her.

327
00:21:55,193 --> 00:21:56,402
Are you making us laugh?

328
00:21:56,694 --> 00:21:57,820
Do you really think.

329
00:21:58,196 --> 00:22:00,156
Supremo can hurt her?

330
00:22:01,366 --> 00:22:02,951
I think it's you who should be nervous.

331
00:22:05,161 --> 00:22:07,205
If Supremo doesn't want to punish her.

332
00:22:09,999 --> 00:22:10,999
I will.

333
00:22:11,584 --> 00:22:13,264
I'll make sure she gets what she deserves.

334
00:22:17,465 --> 00:22:18,465
Don't worry about her.

335
00:22:19,092 --> 00:22:20,510
You didn't mean to hurt him.

336
00:22:21,219 --> 00:22:22,679
This is negligence, Zein!

337
00:22:23,221 --> 00:22:25,056
You endangered the council!

338
00:22:25,306 --> 00:22:26,891
How could you be so careless!

339
00:22:27,433 --> 00:22:29,184
Ms. Kath, I didn't mean to.

340
00:22:29,185 --> 00:22:30,185
Still!

341
00:22:30,436 --> 00:22:31,520
You were so careless!

342
00:22:31,521 --> 00:22:33,121
Can you use that brain
of yours for once!

343
00:22:34,440 --> 00:22:35,440
Ms. Kath

344
00:22:36,067 --> 00:22:37,735
can we all be just calm?

345
00:22:37,819 --> 00:22:38,903
This is not the time

346
00:22:39,904 --> 00:22:40,904
to point fingers.

347
00:22:42,407 --> 00:22:44,158
Let's just have Supremo
take a rest, please.

348
00:23:25,533 --> 00:23:26,659
We heard what happened.

349
00:23:27,176 --> 00:23:28,369
How is Supremo?

350
00:23:30,705 --> 00:23:32,373
He’s still unconscious.

351
00:23:33,332 --> 00:23:34,332
How about you?

352
00:23:34,375 --> 00:23:35,710
Are you okay?

353
00:23:39,797 --> 00:23:41,174
It's my fault.

354
00:23:42,383 --> 00:23:45,053
If I didn't push him to eat vegetables

355
00:23:45,803 --> 00:23:47,138
this would have not happened.

356
00:23:49,057 --> 00:23:52,143
You didn't know he
was allergic to spinach.

357
00:23:52,979 --> 00:23:54,188
It was an accident.

358
00:23:54,905 --> 00:23:55,948
Mia's right.

359
00:23:56,856 --> 00:23:58,691
Don't be too hard on yourself.

360
00:23:59,358 --> 00:24:00,777
Supremo will be okay.

361
00:24:05,031 --> 00:24:05,965
You!

362
00:24:05,990 --> 00:24:07,158
Venomancer!

363
00:24:07,450 --> 00:24:09,452
You need to pay for
what you did to Supremo.

364
00:24:13,831 --> 00:24:15,239
What's happening here?

365
00:24:15,971 --> 00:24:18,932
This is no longer your business,
ex-secretary.

366
00:24:19,967 --> 00:24:21,677
Are you stirring up trouble again?

367
00:24:22,048 --> 00:24:24,841
Our Supremo is unconscious
because of this girl.

368
00:24:24,842 --> 00:24:26,385
He almost died!

369
00:24:27,595 --> 00:24:28,595
What?

370
00:24:28,679 --> 00:24:29,847
I didn't mean to.

371
00:24:31,766 --> 00:24:32,767
Don't play dumb.

372
00:24:33,309 --> 00:24:34,567
You did it on purpose!

373
00:24:34,811 --> 00:24:35,811
No!

374
00:24:36,145 --> 00:24:37,855
I can never hurt Supremo!

375
00:24:38,314 --> 00:24:39,314
Really?

376
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,989
We see right through you!

377
00:24:44,654 --> 00:24:47,406
Are you going to allow
this girl to kill our Supremo?

378
00:24:47,615 --> 00:24:49,700
No!

379
00:24:52,411 --> 00:24:54,121
What should we do to her?

380
00:24:54,122 --> 00:24:55,789
Tie her up and punish her!

381
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:57,124
Right!

382
00:24:57,125 --> 00:24:58,668
Tie her up!

383
00:24:59,544 --> 00:25:01,087
- Zein!
- Don't you dare touch her!

384
00:25:01,212 --> 00:25:02,337
She didn't do it on purpose!

385
00:25:02,338 --> 00:25:03,172
Stop it, guys!

386
00:25:03,172 --> 00:25:04,382
- Let go of me!
- No!

387
00:25:04,382 --> 00:25:05,091
Get over here!

388
00:25:05,091 --> 00:25:06,025
Stop!

389
00:25:06,050 --> 00:25:07,218
Stop resisting!

390
00:25:08,469 --> 00:25:09,762
Let her go.

391
00:25:11,973 --> 00:25:12,973
Zein!

392
00:25:13,224 --> 00:25:14,224
Zein!

393
00:25:14,267 --> 00:25:15,893
- Zein!
- Let her go, please!

394
00:25:16,602 --> 00:25:17,979
- No! Zein!
- Zein!

395
00:25:19,147 --> 00:25:20,147
- Zein!

396
00:25:26,028 --> 00:25:27,113
Hit her again!

397
00:25:28,072 --> 00:25:29,447
Let me go!

398
00:25:29,448 --> 00:25:30,908
- No!
- Zein!

399
00:25:36,289 --> 00:25:37,289
Zein!

400
00:25:37,665 --> 00:25:38,665
Zein!

401
00:25:42,712 --> 00:25:44,255
Hold her and don't let her go!

402
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:56,642
No! Zein!

403
00:25:56,809 --> 00:25:57,809
Zein!

404
00:26:00,855 --> 00:26:01,789
Your turn.

405
00:26:01,814 --> 00:26:02,814
Zein!

406
00:26:04,066 --> 00:26:05,234
Haven't we had enough?

407
00:26:06,736 --> 00:26:08,029
Are you serious, Roxane?

408
00:26:08,863 --> 00:26:10,239
She needs to be punished!

409
00:26:10,406 --> 00:26:12,200
Just think of what she did to Supremo.

410
00:26:12,742 --> 00:26:14,118
She deserves this!

411
00:26:16,746 --> 00:26:17,746
Go!

412
00:26:18,748 --> 00:26:19,748
More!

413
00:26:20,082 --> 00:26:20,750
More!

414
00:26:20,750 --> 00:26:21,392
Zein!

415
00:26:21,417 --> 00:26:22,501
Stop it!

416
00:26:23,127 --> 00:26:24,127
Zein!

417
00:26:24,503 --> 00:26:25,503
More!

418
00:26:28,424 --> 00:26:29,424
Give me that!

419
00:26:29,842 --> 00:26:30,842
You're too weak!

420
00:26:32,929 --> 00:26:34,472
Angelica, stop this!

421
00:26:34,764 --> 00:26:35,973
She's had enough!

422
00:26:36,766 --> 00:26:38,016
Angelica, stop it!

423
00:26:38,017 --> 00:26:39,227
Angelica!

424
00:26:40,895 --> 00:26:42,230
Stop it!

425
00:26:58,246 --> 00:27:00,581
That's what you get
for hurting Supremo!

426
00:27:01,958 --> 00:27:03,292
Should I continue?

427
00:27:03,417 --> 00:27:04,793
- Yes!
- Zein!

428
00:27:04,794 --> 00:27:05,794
Zein!

429
00:27:06,128 --> 00:27:07,588
Stop i! Zein!

430
00:27:10,383 --> 00:27:11,383
Angelica!

431
00:27:13,094 --> 00:27:14,262
Angelica!

432
00:27:14,679 --> 00:27:15,763
Stop!

433
00:27:16,389 --> 00:27:17,390
Please, stop it!

434
00:27:23,437 --> 00:27:25,481
Zein!

435
00:27:25,898 --> 00:27:27,108
What should we do?

436
00:27:27,692 --> 00:27:28,459
Zein!

437
00:27:28,484 --> 00:27:29,484
Zein!

438
00:27:30,820 --> 00:27:32,321
Goodbye, Zein Shion.

439
00:27:34,782 --> 00:27:36,534
Zein!

440
00:27:49,338 --> 00:27:50,715
What do you think you're doing?

441
00:27:51,590 --> 00:27:52,590
Untie her!

442
00:27:58,180 --> 00:27:59,180
All of you!

443
00:28:00,182 --> 00:28:02,143
Take my command!

444
00:28:03,284 --> 00:28:05,661
Nobody leaves this hall.

445
00:28:07,857 --> 00:28:09,607
This is an order

446
00:28:09,608 --> 00:28:11,902
