Student Government President.

447
00:28:12,653 --> 00:28:13,654
Understood?

448
00:28:20,411 --> 00:28:21,412
Let go!

449
00:28:23,414 --> 00:28:24,414
Zein.

450
00:28:30,963 --> 00:28:31,963
Zein...

451
00:28:51,776 --> 00:28:53,110
Hang in there, Zein.

452
00:28:55,154 --> 00:28:57,656
Nurse, what's her blood type?

453
00:28:57,823 --> 00:28:58,823
I don't know.

454
00:29:06,741 --> 00:29:09,035
Extracting blood sample.

455
00:29:41,867 --> 00:29:42,867
Guys...

456
00:29:43,786 --> 00:29:45,329
we heard what happened.

457
00:29:45,496 --> 00:29:46,580
Are you okay?

458
00:29:48,582 --> 00:29:49,875
We're okay

459
00:29:50,751 --> 00:29:52,253
but Zein isn't.

460
00:29:52,878 --> 00:29:54,255
How did it come to that?

461
00:29:54,630 --> 00:29:55,840
Why didn't she fight back?

462
00:29:56,382 --> 00:29:57,842
I think she has a reason.

463
00:29:58,259 --> 00:30:01,762
But right now let's just
hope she'll be okay.

464
00:30:02,722 --> 00:30:03,848
She’ll be okay.

465
00:30:04,223 --> 00:30:05,850
She's with Supremo.

466
00:30:06,851 --> 00:30:08,769
Can't we go to her?

467
00:30:09,437 --> 00:30:10,980
She needs us.

468
00:30:11,147 --> 00:30:12,273
We can't leave.

469
00:30:12,773 --> 00:30:14,275
We can't disobey Supremo's command.

470
00:30:15,860 --> 00:30:16,986
Let's just wait.

471
00:30:17,695 --> 00:30:18,695
Fine.

472
00:30:53,564 --> 00:30:54,607
I promise you.

473
00:30:58,277 --> 00:31:00,946
They will pay for what they did.

474
00:31:28,891 --> 00:31:30,809
You are such a disappointment.

475
00:31:31,602 --> 00:31:34,438
This is your last chance, Supremo!

476
00:31:35,064 --> 00:31:36,064
Do what you want.

477
00:31:37,233 --> 00:31:38,858
I found the source of my happiness

478
00:31:38,859 --> 00:31:40,569
and I'm not going to let it go.

479
00:31:41,612 --> 00:31:43,572
You're exacty like Lux.

480
00:31:45,324 --> 00:31:46,450
Fragile.

481
00:31:46,992 --> 00:31:47,992
Weak.

482
00:31:49,064 --> 00:31:51,275
I'm not Lux.

483
00:31:53,123 --> 00:31:54,416
Are you sure?

484
00:31:55,584 --> 00:31:56,584
Unlike him.

485
00:31:57,795 --> 00:31:58,921
I'm watching my back.

486
00:32:02,466 --> 00:32:03,968
Let's see about that.

487
00:32:05,052 --> 00:32:06,052
Do you think

488
00:32:07,137 --> 00:32:08,764
I'll let you repeat what
you did before?

489
00:32:09,598 --> 00:32:10,891
You're dead wrong.

490
00:32:12,518 --> 00:32:14,019
Try to touch Zein

491
00:32:15,271 --> 00:32:18,148
and you'll feel what
the real hell is like.

492
00:32:19,692 --> 00:32:21,068
Are you trying to scare me?

493
00:32:22,319 --> 00:32:23,319
No.

494
00:32:24,154 --> 00:32:26,073
But if you're planning to hurt her

495
00:32:27,658 --> 00:32:29,034
you should be afraid.

496
00:32:32,329 --> 00:32:33,455
If you say so.

497
00:32:46,218 --> 00:32:46,969
What the fuck, Roxane.

498
00:32:46,970 --> 00:32:49,090
- We need to avenge Zein.
- What are you so afraid of?

499
00:32:49,847 --> 00:32:51,167
- I wonder.
- Aren't you the queen?

500
00:32:51,307 --> 00:32:52,307
How is she?

501
00:32:52,558 --> 00:32:53,725
- She won't stop so we need...

502
00:32:53,726 --> 00:32:55,366
- to finish this.
- She's gonna be fine.

503
00:32:55,519 --> 00:32:57,020
As long as she's with Supremo

504
00:32:57,021 --> 00:32:58,230
she'll be taken care of.

505
00:32:58,856 --> 00:32:59,981
Stop it!

506
00:32:59,982 --> 00:33:01,233
I'm done with you.

507
00:33:02,234 --> 00:33:03,736
Watch your words, Roxane.

508
00:33:04,069 --> 00:33:05,069
Why?

509
00:33:05,112 --> 00:33:06,864
Isn't this your plan?

510
00:33:07,448 --> 00:33:08,073
Right?

511
00:33:08,365 --> 00:33:09,490
You want Zein dead

512
00:33:09,491 --> 00:33:11,091
so you can have
Supremo all for yourself!

513
00:33:13,037 --> 00:33:14,121
How dare you?

514
00:33:14,288 --> 00:33:15,539
I’m the Queen here!

515
00:33:21,211 --> 00:33:22,379
You bitch.

516
00:33:25,466 --> 00:33:26,800
You think you can fight me?

517
00:33:33,098 --> 00:33:34,308
You bitch!

518
00:33:34,767 --> 00:33:36,185
Really? You're done with me?

519
00:33:37,186 --> 00:33:38,646
No one's going to stop me.

520
00:33:38,854 --> 00:33:39,980
You bitch!

521
00:33:45,819 --> 00:33:47,529
The BBG...

522
00:33:51,367 --> 00:33:52,868
It's about time they stop fighting.

523
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:08,384
Why did you anger him?

524
00:34:15,432 --> 00:34:17,685
If you only saw how
angry Supremo was earlier

525
00:34:18,268 --> 00:34:19,770
you should be afraid.

526
00:34:23,899 --> 00:34:25,359
It's Raze...

527
00:34:26,568 --> 00:34:27,568
What the...

528
00:34:27,736 --> 00:34:29,029
Devil God Warrior?

529
00:34:31,699 --> 00:34:32,699
Raze.

530
00:34:33,492 --> 00:34:34,492
Please Raze.

531
00:34:35,536 --> 00:34:36,536
You have to help me.

532
00:34:36,662 --> 00:34:37,392
Please.

533
00:34:37,417 --> 00:34:38,417
Sorry...

534
00:34:38,580 --> 00:34:40,666
but I can't do anything about this.

535
00:34:41,509 --> 00:34:42,509
What?

536
00:34:44,753 --> 00:34:45,753
Huh?

537
00:34:47,297 --> 00:34:48,297
Supremo?

538
00:34:50,217 --> 00:34:51,217
Get back.

539
00:34:55,222 --> 00:34:56,222
Supremo...

540
00:34:57,474 --> 00:34:58,225
I'm sorry.

541
00:34:58,226 --> 00:34:59,852
I won't do it again.

542
00:35:00,227 --> 00:35:01,854
Forgive me, please.

543
00:35:02,229 --> 00:35:02,896
Supremo.

544
00:35:02,897 --> 00:35:04,523
I am not asking you to apologize.

545
00:35:04,690 --> 00:35:05,566
Forgive me, please.

546
00:35:05,649 --> 00:35:07,818
I just want you to pay
for the consequences.

547
00:35:08,610 --> 00:35:09,819
Consequences?

548
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:11,029
Or you're just angry

549
00:35:11,030 --> 00:35:13,365
because your favorite
secretary got hurt?

550
00:35:16,910 --> 00:35:17,910
Huh?

551
00:35:18,245 --> 00:35:20,873
I'm Supremo's favorite secretary.

552
00:35:21,331 --> 00:35:22,331
Don't butt it.

553
00:35:22,624 --> 00:35:24,376
Supremo never had your back.

554
00:35:26,545 --> 00:35:30,340
Every student involved in
the commotion eariler

555
00:35:31,383 --> 00:35:32,760
