556
00:35:33,385 --> 00:35:35,095
Who are you to do this to us?

557
00:35:35,429 --> 00:35:37,181
I am the Queen here!

558
00:35:38,474 --> 00:35:41,810
Not anymore!

559
00:35:43,270 --> 00:35:44,354
What the fuck.

560
00:35:45,230 --> 00:35:46,230
What is he doing?

561
00:35:48,901 --> 00:35:50,693
Who'll be the next queen?

562
00:35:50,694 --> 00:35:51,694
Huh?

563
00:35:51,987 --> 00:35:52,987
Queen?

564
00:37:23,912 --> 00:37:25,122
Starting today

565
00:37:25,998 --> 00:37:28,083
there will be no queen from DGW!

566
00:37:29,543 --> 00:37:32,337
I am giving the
crown to Zein Shion.

567
00:37:32,379 --> 00:37:33,379
To Zein?

568
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,797
As the new queen of Hell University.

569
00:37:34,798 --> 00:37:35,798
Zein?

570
00:37:40,596 --> 00:37:41,889
Really?

571
00:37:42,389 --> 00:37:44,558
Zein is the new queen
of Hell University?

572
00:37:44,933 --> 00:37:46,226
You can’t do that!

573
00:37:47,144 --> 00:37:48,145
Of course I can!

574
00:37:55,611 --> 00:37:57,237
And I also declare

575
00:37:57,571 --> 00:37:58,614
Matthew Hart

576
00:37:59,323 --> 00:38:02,451
as the new King of Hell University.

577
00:38:05,370 --> 00:38:06,370
Matt?

578
00:38:07,623 --> 00:38:10,751
SUBS TO FOLOW ONCE ADR IS PLACED

